# CCY Container Session State Directory
#
# This directory stores Claude Code user-level state for CCY containers:
# - Session history (history.jsonl)
# - Project databases (projects/)
# - Todo lists (todos/)
# - Cache files (cache/)
# - File history (file-history/)
#
# The container symlinks /root/.claude -> /workspace/.claude/ccy/
# This keeps containers ephemeral while persisting sessions in the project.
#
# IMPORTANT: This directory should NEVER be committed to git
# (except this .gitignore and custom Dockerfile if present)

# Ignore everything in this directory
*

# Except this .gitignore (provides documentation and safety)
!.gitignore

# And custom Dockerfile (project-specific container extensions)
!Dockerfile
